I serve as an Assistant Professor in the Department of Journalism and Mass Communication at Fatima College in Madurai. In this role, I have the opportunity to educate and inspire the next generation of media professionals. My teaching focuses on print, electronic, and visual media, equipping students with the knowledge and skills they need to thrive in the rapidly evolving media landscape.
Furthermore, to stay ahead of the curve and expand my expertise, I am currently exploring the exciting realm of web3 as a Digital Marketer and content creator. I am affiliated with Recorem, a web3 company that embraces the potential of emerging technologies. This exploration allows me to harness the power of the digital space, employ innovative marketing strategies, and create engaging content that resonates with audiences.
